醋酸/醋酸铝溶液可用于治疗外耳道感染。 这种药物可以阻止细菌和真菌的生长，并有益地干燥耳道。 <ref>Medicine Net. [http://www.medicinenet.com/acetic_acid_with_aluminum_acetate-otic/article.htm "Acetic Acid/Aluminum Acetate - OTIC (Domeboro) Side Effects, Medical Uses, and Drug Interactions."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.medicinenet.com/acetic_acid_with_aluminum_acetate-otic/article.htm |date=20200813121048 }} MedicineNet. N.p., n.d. Web. 08 Oct 2012.</ref> 美国可以制备此药物的地方包括Domeboro Otic，Star-Otic和Borofair。 <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.drugs.com/cdi/acetic-acid-aluminum-acetate-solution.html |title=Drugs.com: Acetic acid/ aluminum acetate solution |accessdate=2020-07-27 |archive-date=2016-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820181536/https://www.drugs.com/cdi/acetic-acid-aluminum-acetate-solution.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==媒染剂==
